'''''The Empire Strikes Back Monthly'' 156''' is the one hundred fifty-sixth issue of the ''[[The Empire Strikes Back Monthly]]'' series of comic reprints, published in [[May]] [[1982]].

This issue includes one of the few original comic stories in the series, "[[Rust Never Sleeps]]". It was later reprinted and colorized in [[Classic Star Wars: Devilworlds 2|''Classic Star Wars: Devilworlds'' 2]].

